Survival Room
A top-down zombie survival game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Survive the horde for as long as you can!

Play the Live Demo!
https://hamza2523.github.io/Survival-Room-Game/

How to Play
Move: WASD or Arrow Keys

Aim: Mouse

Shoot/Attack: Left-click

Switch Weapon: 1, 2, or Scroll Wheel

Reload: R

Pause: P

Look out for power-ups like Health Packs and Rage Packs to help you survive longer!

How to Run Locally
Clone or download the repository.

Open the index.html file in your browser.
